revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Line_Horizon}}
{{Special|9|no parameters required|Renderer|use=line}}

This special is to be placed on a line in the map, which is then “extended” into infinity. It will only create an infinite view on that particular line, so you may need to place it on multiple lines to get the desired effect. Useful for [[skybox|skyboxes]]. Do not use with [[slopes]]!

==Examples==
{{noexamples}}

== Conversions from linedef types ==
The following Doom map format types can be converted as Line Horizon:
{| {{prettytable}}
!Type!!Conversion!!Trigger
|-
|{{icon|ZDoom}} 337:Line Horizon||Line_Horizon ()||
|-
|{{icon|Eternity}} 450:Line Horizon||Line_Horizon ()||
|}

